OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,FThe head of the Independent Commission
OL,7,Ffor Reconciliation and Information
OL,8,FRecovery (ICRIR) has told MPs that a
OL,9,FGovernment 'reset' of the
OL,10,Fcontroversial Legacy Act , could
OL,11,Finclude the appointment of an Irish
OL,12,FCommissioner to assist with the
OL,13,Forganisation's discovery of
OL,14,Finformation into Troubles killings.
OL,16,FThe ICRIR, which is currently
OL,17,Fconducting 60 investigations, also
OL,18,Fsaid it wants the power to challenge
OL,19,Fthe government withholding
OL,20,Fdocumentation under national security
OL,21,Fconcerns.
