OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,FSir Declan Morgan, chief commissioner
OL,7,Fof the ICRIR described a "reset
OL,8,Fmoment" to improve the "imperfect"
OL,9,FLegacy Act.
OL,11,FIt comes after the controversial
OL,12,Flegislation was passed despite
OL,13,Fwidespread opposition and concern from
OL,14,Fpolitical parties in Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fand victims and survivors of the
OL,16,FTroubles.
OL,18,FThe Legacy Act halted scores of cases
OL,19,Fgoing through the courts and inquests
OL,20,Fconcerning the Troubles.
