OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,FGiving evidence to the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Affairs Committee over how the
OL,8,FGovernment should address the region's
OL,9,Fpast, Sir Declan said the ICRIR has
OL,10,Freceived more than 160 requests.
OL,12,FThose include the deaths of five
OL,13,Fpeople in the IRA's Guildford pub
OL,14,Fbombings in 1974, the death of
OL,15,FAlexander Millar in Ardoyne in 1975,
OL,16,Fthe death of Seamus Bradley shot by
OL,17,Fthe Army in Londonderry in 1972 and
OL,18,Fthe death of the judge Rory Conaghan
OL,19,Fkilled by the IRA in 1975.
