OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,F"By the end of this year we will have
OL,7,Fover 100 investigations in relation to
OL,8,Fprobably more than 150 deaths ongoing,
OL,9,Fand by the time of the legislation we
OL,10,Fwould expect that that number would
OL,11,Fhave significantly increased, as would
OL,12,Fthe number of people that we have been
OL,13,Fable to help.
OL,15,F"The choice was whether to help those
OL,16,Fpeople who were anxious to have an
OL,17,Fanswer to what they wanted or stand
OL,18,Fback and say, this legislation is not
OL,19,Fperfect. I don't make any apology for
OL,20,Fthe fact that I decided I wanted to
OL,21,Fhelp people."
