OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,FHe added: "I just wonder whether the
OL,7,Fapproach to the work of the commission
OL,8,Fwill be treated in such a negative
OL,9,Flight, particularly when the two
OL,10,Fgovernments reach agreement on what
OL,11,Fthey want to do."
OL,13,FAlso giving evidence to the committee,
OL,14,FICRIR commissioner for investigations
OL,15,FPeter Sheridan said he absolutely
OL,16,Frejects that they are carrying out
OL,17,Flight-touch reviews.
OL,19,F"Let me assure this committee that it
OL,20,Fis absolutely not," he told MPs.
