OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,FHe described the first stage of the
OL,7,Fprocess as being a cold case review
OL,8,Fwhich looks for new evidence, verifies
OL,9,Fold evidence, identifies investigative
OL,10,Ffailures and re-examines forensics.
OL,12,F"That's going to be the key for us
OL,13,Fbecause witness evidence from the past
OL,14,Fis difficult, but new forensic
OL,15,Fopportunities, and I already see it in
OL,16,Fsome of the cases ... so we're
OL,17,Fexamining that with the latest trace
OL,18,Fevidence that you can use," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUzD@[O]
