OL,3,CLegacy body capable of uncovering
OL,4,C'unvarnished truth', says ICRIR chief
OL,6,F"Looking at continuity of evidence in
OL,7,Fold cases, conduct fresh searches on
OL,8,Fdata bases and use advances in digital
OL,9,Fforensics, so it is absolutely not a
OL,10,Flight-touch review.
OL,12,F"I am duty-bound under the legislation
OL,13,Fto look into all of the circumstances
OL,14,Fof the case, that's what we're doing."
OL,16,FSir Declan emphasised that the focus
OL,17,Fof the ICRIR is "on finding a
OL,18,Fmechanism to ensure that we achieve
OL,19,Fthe unvarnished truth for victims and
OL,20,Fsurvivors".
