OL,6,FSteven Bramley, general counsel at the
OL,7,FICRIR, added that the areas they want
OL,8,Fto reform include greater independent
OL,9,Foversight; a statutory voice for
OL,10,Fvictims and survivors; statutory
OL,11,Finvestigations, not reviews; a
OL,12,Fstatutory conflict of interest policy;
OL,13,Fa self initiation power where there is
OL,14,Fa thematic link between different
OL,15,Fevents; and "a power for chief
OL,16,Fconstables to refer cases directly to
OL,17,Fus when new evidence comes to light".
